<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Confirmación de Compra - GetInMotion</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2B2B2B 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
        }
        .logo {
            height: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .success-badge {
            background: #D4FF00;
            color: #2B2B2B;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .content {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-left: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-right: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #2B2B2B;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .order-summary {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #D4FF00;
        }
        .order-summary h3 {
            color: #2B2B2B;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .order-info {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .order-info:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .order-info-label {
            color: #888;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .order-info-value {
            color: #2B2B2B;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .items-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .items-table th {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #2B2B2B;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .items-table td {
            padding: 15px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .items-table tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .item-name {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #2B2B2B;
        }
        .item-quantity {
            text-align: center;
            color: #888;
        }
        .item-price {
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2B2B2B;
        }
        .total-row {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .total-row td {
            padding: 15px 12px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #2B2B2B;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background: #e3f2fd;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .next-steps h3 {
            color: #1976d2;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .next-steps ul {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .next-steps li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 35px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #D4FF00;
            color: #2B2B2B;
            padding: 16px 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(212, 255, 0, 0.3);
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            color: #888;
            font-size: 13px;
            border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .footer-emoji {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 0 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            {{#if logoUrl}}
            <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="GetInMotion" class="logo">
            {{/if}}
            <h1>¡Compra Confirmada!</h1>
            <span class="success-badge">✓ Pago Exitoso</span>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">¡Gracias por tu compra, {{buyerName}}! 🎉</div>
            <p class="message">
                Tu pago ha sido procesado exitosamente. Hemos recibido tu pedido y pronto comenzaremos a prepararlo.
            </p>

            <div class="order-summary">
                <h3>📋 Resumen del Pedido</h3>
                <div class="order-info">
                    <span class="order-info-label">ID del Carrito:</span>
                    <span class="order-info-value">{{cartId}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="order-info">
                    <span class="order-info-label">ID de Transacción:</span>
                    <span class="order-info-value">{{transactionId}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="order-info">
                    <span class="order-info-label">Moneda:</span>
                    <span class="order-info-value">{{currency}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: #2B2B2B; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px;">🛍️ Productos Comprados</h3>

            <table class="items-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Producto</th>
                        <th style="text-align: center;">Cantidad</th>
                        <th style="text-align: right;">Precio Unitario</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {{#each items}}
                    <tr>
                        <td class="item-name">{{this.productName}}</td>
                        <td class="item-quantity">{{this.quantity}}</td>
                        <td class="item-price">{{this.formattedPrice}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                </tbody>
                <tfoot>
                    <tr class="total-row">
                        <td colspan="2">Total</td>
                        <td class="item-price">{{totalFormatted}}</td>
                    </tr>
                </tfoot>
            </table>

            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>📦 Próximos Pasos</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Recibirás un correo con el número de seguimiento cuando tu pedido sea enviado</li>
                    <li>Los artesanos comenzarán a preparar tus productos</li>
                    <li>Puedes ver el estado de tu pedido en tu cuenta</li>
                    <li>Si tienes alguna pregunta, contáctanos y te ayudaremos</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{ordersUrl}}" class="button">Ver mis pedidos</a>
            </div>

            <p class="message">
                Si tienes alguna pregunta sobre tu pedido, no dudes en contactarnos.
            </p>
            <p class="message">
                ¡Gracias por apoyar a nuestros artesanos!
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Con cariño desde Bogotá, Colombia <span class="footer-emoji">🇨🇴</span></p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px;">GetInMotion © {{year}}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
